data.title: Health Pass Sertifika
data.meta_description: Health Pass Sertifika - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document is a digital COVID vaccination certificate for Jeyhun Ramazanov with a date of birth of 1997-04-19. It certifies that he received the first of two doses of the Coronavac vaccine in Turkey on 2021-01-21. The certificate was issued by the Ministry of Health of the Republic of Turkey and contains identifying information like a unique ID number.
